%% RHOAI Operator (rhods-operator) - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Envoy as Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP TLS Terminate
    participant KAP as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth/OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Backend Service<br/>(via HTTPRoute)

    Note over User,Backend: Flow 1: User Access to RHOAI Dashboard (Gateway API Mode)

    User->>Router: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Router->>Envoy: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS Terminate
    Envoy->>KAP: ext_authz check<br/>HTTPS/8443 (service-CA TLS)<br/>Cookie/Bearer token
    KAP->>OAuth: Validate credentials<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Client credentials
    OAuth-->>KAP: Auth response
    KAP-->>Envoy: Auth decision + identity
    Note over Envoy: Lua filter strips OAuth cookies,<br/>sets Bearer authorization header
    Envoy->>Backend: Forward request<br/>HTTPS (SIMPLE via DestinationRule)<br/>Bearer token forwarded
    Backend-->>Envoy: Response
    Envoy-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,Backend: Flow 2: Legacy Dashboard URL Redirect

    participant LegacyRouter as OpenShift Router<br/>(legacy Route)
    participant Nginx as dashboard-redirect<br/>nginx 8080/TCP

    User->>LegacyRouter: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS (edge)
    LegacyRouter->>Nginx: HTTP/8080
    Nginx-->>User: 301 Redirect to<br/>https://rh-ai.{domain}

    Note over User,Backend: Flow 3: Operator Reconciliation

    participant Operator as rhods-operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Manifests as Component Manifests<br/>(embedded /opt/manifests)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch CRDs (DSC, DSCI)<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: CR change event
    Operator->>Manifests: Load component manifests<br/>(filesystem)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update resources<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token (RBAC)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resource status
